cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is about a real-time multi-object tracking system that incorporates appearance embedding into a single-shot detector. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. Additionally, the paper involves multi-task learning, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category. The system also deals with tracking objects in real-time, which could be related to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
